First we can recompile the Avro schemas into Java code using the following commands:
cd lib/
java -jar avro-tools-1.7.7.jar compile -string protocol ../src/chat.avpr ../src/
java -jar avro−tools−1.7.7.jar compile -string protocol ../src/chatClientServer.avpr ../src/

Then we imported the whole project into Eclipse as an existing Java project 
and run both avro.chat.server/Server and avro.chat.client/Client respectively.